summary.p:
The volume contains Eric Benzelius, Diarium Vazstenense, Uppsala 1721 , with annotations by Johan Helin (see slip on ), and Woodcuts of Graves in Vadstena Abbey Church by Elias Brenner
, with annotations by Helin. See also Fm 34.
